name: Lucha
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Luchadores.io is an upcoming play to earn auto battler where you can fight it out against other players Lucha Libre style!
Just like the Luchador NFTs themselves, the gameplay mechanics will be 100% onchain so  these Luchas can battle for as long as the blockchain stands.
